Former  Dell Inc . Global Supply
Manager Daniel DeVore told a judge at his plea hearing in
Manhattan federal court that he leaked material inside
information to clients of Guidepoint Global LLC, a consulting
and research firm based in New York. DeVore also said he leaked
insider information to Primary Global LLC and Vista Corp.,
according to a transcript of his hearing. DeVore pleaded guilty
to fraud charges Dec. 10.  A call to Guidepoint for comment wasnâ€™t immediately
